  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA376-kiḷavi">itu tōḻi kiḷi mēlvaittuc ciṟaippuṟamākac colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what the confidante said when [HE] was behind the fence, putting it on the parakeet.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA376">
<l>            muṟañcevi yāṉait taṭakaiyiṟ ṟaṭaii</l>
<l>            yiṟaiñciya kurala paintāṭ centiṉai</l>
<l>            varaiyōṉ vaṇmai pōlap palavuṭaṉ</l>
<l>            kiḷaiyō ṭuṇṇum vaḷaivāyp pāciṉaṅ</l>
<l>            kullai kuḷavi kūtaḷaṅ kuvaḷai</l>
<l>            yillamoṭu miṭainta vīrntaṇ kaṇṇiyaṉ</l>
<l>            cuṟṟamai villaṉ ceyalait tōṉṟu</l>
<l>            naṟṟār mārpaṟ kāṇkuṟiṟ ciṟiya</l>
<l>            naṟkavaṟ kaṟiya vuraimiṉ piṟṟai</l>
<l>            yaṇaṅku maṇaṅkum pōlu maṇaṅki</l>
<l>            vaṟumpuṉaṅ kāval viṭāmai</l>
<l>            yaṟintaṉi rallirō vaṟaṉil yāyē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>            O green flock with curved beak that eats with [its] relations,</l>
<l rend="indent">            many together, as if from the liberality of one without limit,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            of the red millet with greens stalks [and] bowed ears,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            bending down like the broad trunk of a winnow-eared elephant</l>
<l rend="indent">            if you catch sight of him with a good garland on his chest,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            who appears by the Aśoka tree with a bow tied close around(?) [him]</l>
<l rend="indent3">            [and] with a wet cool chaplet in which with the Illam,</l>
<l rend="indent3">            hemp, wild jasmine, Kūtaḷ [and] blue waterlily are set close,</l>
<l>        talk to him a little, so that he knows well:</l>
<l>        Haven’t you understood that [our] dutiful/virtueless mother</l>
<l rend="indent2">            won’t let [us] guard the poor field afterwards,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            tormenting [us] as if all the torments together(?)?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
